&lt;li&gt;Support contract negotiations and deal structuring for programmatic and reseller agreements, partnering with senior leadership on strategic or high-value terms&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead day-to-day programmatic trafficking within SSP platforms, including deal setup, floor pricing, targeting parameters, and troubleshooting delivery or discrepancy issues&lt;/li&gt;
