&lt;li&gt;Maintain an up-to-date database of existing and new partners across programmatic and reseller channels&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with internal teams, including finance, marketing, product, and legal to ensure that advertising initiatives are aligned with the company’s overall strategy&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide regular reporting on partner performance, revenue growth, and operational health&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Stay current on industry trends, ad tech developments, and best practices, sharing insights with internal teams and partners&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
