&lt;li&gt;6+ years of experience in programmatic advertising, with hands-on experience in SSP trafficking and campaign/deal management&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong technical understanding of programmatic infrastructure, including DSPs, SSPs, ad servers, deal/PMP setup, and floor pricing mechanics&lt;/li&gt;
