&lt;li&gt;Strong analytical and problem-solving skills, with the ability to identify trends and act on data&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to work independently and as part of a cross-functional team, with a strong sense of accountability and ownership&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to excel in a fast-paced, exciting environment while maintaining an unwavering dedication to quality work.&lt;/li&gt;
