&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own and evolve the core business scorecards, dashboards, and ad-hoc analyses leaders use to monitor subscriber growth, revenue, billing health, retention, engagement, content performance, and monetization trends.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Translate ambiguous questions from stakeholders into structured analytical plans, clear findings, and actionable recommendations that inform real decisions.&lt;/li&gt;
