&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;ML Vision and Roadmap:&lt;/strong&gt; Contribute to the strategic planning of the recommendations roadmap, aligning engineering efforts with business objectives and user needs.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Explore advanced architectures:&lt;/strong&gt; Experience with frameworks like Two-Tower models and Deep Cross Networks (DCN) is a strong plus.&lt;/li&gt;
